= Appendix A — Source Texts & Recommended Reading

#hm-note[
  This appendix lists every text integrated into the curriculum, organised by function. The code column matches the abbreviations used throughout the monthly syllabi. Student-facing texts are those the student directly reads; Headmaster-only texts inform pedagogy but are not assigned to students. Proprietary materials (QMed/QTar) are presented to students in reworded form only — original lesson documents are never issued directly.
]

#v(0.5em)

